headline: Exploring Analyst Estimates for CarMax (KMX) Q1 Earnings, Beyond Revenue and EPS
summary: Beyond analysts' top -and-bottom-line estimates for CarMax (KMX), evaluate projections for some of its key metrics to gain a better insight into how the business might have performed for the quarter ended May 2025.
